name 'U2L18 FR why is asymmetric encryption useful'
title 'Asymmetric Encryption - why is it useful'
question 'Why is asymmetric encryption useful?'

markdown <<MARKDOWN
In symmetric encryption the same key is used to encrypt and decrypt a message.
In **a**symmetric encryption different keys are used to encrypt and decrypt.

Give at least one (more are welcome) reason why **a**symmetric encryption is useful?
